Class Tile

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.shlomi.golemland.game.Core.Entitys.Tile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ITileChars, Settings
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Cake, Mob, TNT

    public class Tile
extends java.lang.Object
implements ITileChars, Settings
    Tile class is the core of the game. Every map has some tiles. Each tile has vertical and horizontal indexes. It also has X,Y coordinates
    Author:
    Shlomi
